<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q40_v8" title="Q40_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Dos compañías de telefonía móvil ofrecen planes de datos que dependen de la cantidad de días de uso <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math>.</p>
    <p>Para calcular la cantidad total de datos (en MB), se usan las siguientes expresiones en función de <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math>:
    <br/>Compañía A: <m:math><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math>
    <br/>Compañía B: <m:math><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mi>d</m:mi></m:math></p>
    <p>Se sabe que, para 20 días de uso (es decir, cuando <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>), ambas compañías entregan exactamente la misma cantidad total de datos.</p>
    <p>¿Cuál debe ser el valor del bono inicial b de la Compañía B para que esto ocurra?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">300<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para 20 días, la Compañía A entrega <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math> MB. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la Compañía B entrega <m:math><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>300</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:math> MB. Como <m:math><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>, este valor no satisface el problema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">1200<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para 20 días, la Compañía A entrega <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math> MB. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la Compañía B entrega <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2500</m:mn></m:math> MB. Como <m:math><m:mn>2500</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>, este valor no permite que ambas compañías entreguen la misma cantidad de datos.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">1500<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Para 20 días, la Compañía A entrega <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math> MB. Entonces la Compañía B debe cumplir <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>. Al despejar, <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">2800<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Para 20 días, la Compañía A entrega <m:math><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math> MB. Si <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>, entonces la Compañía B entrega <m:math><m:mn>2800</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4100</m:mn></m:math> MB. Como <m:math><m:mn>4100</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math>, este valor no cumple la condición dada.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Calcular la cantidad de datos de la Compañía A para 20 días</strong></p>
            <p>Sustituimos <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math> en la expresión de la Compañía A:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>80</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1200</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1600</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, para 20 días, la Compañía A entrega 2800 MB.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Igualar la expresión de la Compañía B a 2800 MB</strong></p>
            <p>Como ambas compañías entregan exactamente la misma cantidad de datos cuando <m:math><m:mi>d</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, en la Compañía B debe cumplirse:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Resolver la ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>Calculamos:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>65</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Restamos 1300 a ambos lados:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2800</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>1300</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El valor del bono inicial de la Compañía B debe ser <m:math><m:mi>b</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1500</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>La alternativa correcta es la <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>